{"tid":868263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(後續發展)被同事帶去時鐘酒店幫手機充電被姦 被告罪成","createTime":"2018-10-19T10:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T12:00:40.000Z","uid":31798,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f2561f73bcae52904146355a4a1ea78fe165764","tid":868263,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:23:35.000Z","msg":"賓館內強姦新上班女同事 已婚新移民被一致裁定罪成<br />\n<br />\n4歲戲院女票務員上班第二日即有已婚男同事邀約睇戲，又向她發放色情影片，及後睇戲前她因手機沒電，男方帶她上所住的賓館取手機充電器，期間遭對方強姦。陪審團退庭商議4小時後，一致裁定被告強姦罪成。案件押後至10月27日再訊，期間先為女事主索取創傷報告。<br />\n去年5月始從內地來港定居的被告羅善強（34歲），被裁定同年9月4日，在旺角金泉酒店一間房內強姦事主X。控方指被告已婚，育有一對分別6歲及2歲的子女。被告來港居住後，於7月起租住旺角金泉酒店。<br />\n控方指X上班的第二天，被告已邀請X看電影，又發送一段色情影片和一幅色情卡通圖片給她，又問她看罷有沒有感覺，「你唔會睇咗冇感覺嘅，我就有點」。X稱沒下載影片，並刪掉圖片，當被告是普通同事。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">X答應與被告睇戲，但兩人看戲前先到被告入住的賓館，全因X稱手機沒電，被告提議到賓館拿手機充電器，期間被告突然在床上播放色情影片，之後再強吻X及強姦她。被告完事後落樓買水予X，X即伺機離開賓館向軍裝警員求助。</span>被告警誡下承認：「阿Sir，我只係錫過佢，揸過佢個波，同用手撩過佢下面。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181019/58812624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181019%2F58812624&d=JNKOYaxhaqxPleht%2BagRYxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=9b4a2d58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181019%2F58812624&h=a4c2e4f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181019/58812624</a><br />\n<br />\n上一個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/857651/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/857651/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n呢d案永遠都係男人冇著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c02291a7b224514479a2ff7bc5db50bd700910","tid":868263,"uid":101714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:24:11.000Z","msg":"4歲戲院女票務員上班第二日即有已婚男同事邀約睇戲"},{"pid":"14ad402dc0b4698cf4c810985625f611b5bcabce","tid":868263,"uid":31439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b652cb5d5d91b82ea50aea927f8b40a35bb31ea3","tid":868263,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14ad402dc0b4698cf4c810985625f611b5bcabce","tid":868263,"uid":31439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"童工都要報警啦"},{"pid":"0b9f34989de23dd6fd91b74f6eb478de61c1fd56","tid":868263,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"36c02291a7b224514479a2ff7bc5db50bd700910","tid":868263,"uid":101714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:24:11.000Z","msg":"4歲戲院女票務員上班第二日即有已婚男同事邀約睇戲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"24<br />\nCopy漏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034c557b4410786221f28652d49ca280fb2066f1","tid":868263,"uid":4168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"我真係點睇都覺係一對男女去爆房，係咪冇俾錢或者俾慢咗呀？"},{"pid":"78ef2ba1cb18f4ef8140f74822093b68f7d3405c","tid":868263,"uid":61271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"034c557b4410786221f28652d49ca280fb2066f1","tid":868263,"uid":4168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"我真係點睇都覺係一對男女去爆房，係咪冇俾錢或者俾慢咗呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:26:51.000Z","msg":"應該係知道左個男人有老婆仔女"},{"pid":"2a3e2045ac0ac4736a9e1fb5937ad8c3b4d844b0","tid":868263,"uid":2567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:27:31.000Z","msg":"4歲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91dad002bb5493fb7065bb129142b33046cf42f","tid":868263,"uid":34976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"被告警誡下承認：「阿Sir，我只係錫過佢